    "notes": "Alert on: (1) repeated connections to same non-CDN IP:port with consistent small byte counts and short duration, OR (2) known malicious JA3 hashes (e7d705a3286e19ea42f587b344ee6865 is associated with Cobalt Strike/Mythic). Beacon detection requires time-series aggregation — threshold: 3+ connections to same dest within 5 minutes with stddev(bytes) < 100."
